      "statement": "theorem procedural_associator_cocycle_8a9aaaa57b0e : (\u2200 lemma_p0_p83dfa0 : Prop,\n    lemma_p0_p83dfa0 \u2192\n      (\u2200 {R : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocRing R] (a b c d : R),\n        a * associator b c d - associator (a * b) c d + associator a (b * c) d - associator a b (c * d) +\n            associator a b c * d =\n          0)) \u2227\n  (\u2200 {R : Type _} {S : Type _} [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring R] [NonUnitalNonAssocSemiring S] (f : R \u2192+ S),\n    (\u2200 (x y : R), f (x * y) = f x * f y) \u2194 AddMonoidHom.mul.compr\u2082 f = (AddMonoidHom.mul.comp f).compl\u2082 f) := by\n  sorry",
